@startuml auth_project_dashboard_sequence
title Sequence Diagram - Authentication and Project Dashboard

actor "User" as U
participant "React SPA" as FE
participant "Spring Security" as SEC
participant "Google Workspace OIDC" as GWS
participant "Auth Module" as AM
participant "Project API" as PA
participant "Authorization Service" as AZ
database "PostgreSQL" as PG
participant "Audit Service" as AS

U -> FE: Open application
FE -> AM: GET /api/v1/auth/me
AM -> SEC: Resolve authenticated principal

alt No active session
  SEC --> FE: 401 UNAUTHENTICATED
  FE -> SEC: Redirect to OAuth login
  SEC -> GWS: Authorization request
  GWS --> SEC: Authorization code and ID token
  SEC -> AM: Map Google identity by email
  AM -> PG: Upsert or load user by email
  PG --> AM: User profile and role
  AM -> AS: Record LOGIN
  AS -> PG: Insert audit log
  SEC --> FE: Set session and redirect
else Active session
  SEC --> AM: Current user principal
end

AM --> FE: 200 CurrentUser

U -> FE: Open Project Dashboard
FE -> PA: GET /api/v1/projects
PA -> SEC: Resolve current user
PA -> AZ: Authorize project list
AZ --> PA: Allowed with ownership scope
PA -> PG: Query visible projects
PG --> PA: Project summaries
PA --> FE: ProjectPage
FE --> U: Render dashboard

@enduml
